00:30:43.667 --> 00:30:46.325
BUT FIRST. WE'VE GOT
A NEW MEMBER

696
00:30:46.409 --> 00:30:48.153
TO WELCOME TO OUR BROTHERHOOD...

697
00:30:48.237 --> 00:30:49.589
MR. RUSSELL TAN.

698
00:30:49.673 --> 00:30:51.980
THAT IS. IF HE CAN PASS
THE FINAL TRIAL.

699
00:30:54.939 --> 00:30:57.858
YOU SEE. RUSSELL.
NOT ALL WHO ARE INVITED

700
00:30:57.942 --> 00:31:00.078
TO JOIN OUR RANKS MAKE THE CUT.

701
00:31:00.162 --> 00:31:04.909
THERE IS ONE FINAL STEP BEFORE
YOUR INITIATION IS COMPLETE.

702
00:31:04.993 --> 00:31:07.825
A TEST. OF SORTS.

703
00:31:07.909 --> 00:31:11.089
OF YOUR WORTHINESS
IN THE EYES OF YOUR PEERS.

704
00:31:11.173 --> 00:31:13.961
YOU MUST FIRST CORRECTLY
ANSWER THE RIDDLES

705
00:31:14.045 --> 00:31:15.742
OF THE INNER SANCTUM.

706
00:31:17.092 --> 00:31:19.575
APOLOGIES IF WE'RE
CATCHING YOU OFF GUARD.

707
00:31:19.659 --> 00:31:22.013
BUT THIS IS A TEST EACH
AND EVERY ONE OF OUR MEMBERS

708
00:31:22.097 --> 00:31:23.362
HAS ALREADY PASSED.

709
00:31:23.446 --> 00:31:25.146
IT'S A TEST
OF YOUR CUNNING.

710
00:31:25.230 --> 00:31:27.453
PREPARATION.
AND FORESIGHT...

711
00:31:27.537 --> 00:31:29.759
OF YOUR ABILITY TO
FORGE RELATIONSHIPS

712
00:31:29.843 --> 00:31:33.067
WITH THE MEN WHOSE SOCIETY
YOU SEEK TO JOIN.

713
00:31:33.151 --> 00:31:34.939
NATHAN: ARE YOU READY?
RUSSELL: YES.

714
00:31:35.023 --> 00:31:37.680
ALL RIGHT. THEN.
WHY DO WE TRUST THE GIFTS

715
00:31:37.764 --> 00:31:39.766
JACOB SLOAN BEQUEATHED
TO US?

716
00:31:40.767 --> 00:31:42.555
RUSSELL: BECAUSE HE ALONE

717
00:31:42.639 --> 00:31:45.558
UNDERSTOOD THE TRUE
NATURE OF THE WORLD.

718
00:31:45.642 --> 00:31:47.861
[CROWD MURMURING]

719
00:31:50.429 --> 00:31:53.305
CORRECT.
THE SECOND QUESTION.

720
00:31:53.389 --> 00:31:54.784
WHAT DID JACOB SLOAN SEE

721
00:31:54.868 --> 00:31:57.135
WHEN HE PEERED
THROUGH THE VEIL?

722
00:31:57.219 --> 00:31:59.137
RUSSELL: THE LINE BEYOND.

723
00:31:59.221 --> 00:32:01.875
BETWEEN LIFE AND DEATH.

724
00:32:02.833 --> 00:32:04.272
[WHISPERING] NICKY.
WE'RE RUNNING OUT OF TIME.

725
00:32:04.356 --> 00:32:05.970
[WHISPERING] I KNOW. I KNOW.

726
00:32:06.054 --> 00:32:09.451
NATHAN: THE THIRD
AND FINAL RIDDLE.

727
00:32:09.535 --> 00:32:12.672
HOW SHOULD WE BEST HONOR
JACOB SLOAN'S MEMORY?

728
00:32:12.756 --> 00:32:17.068
BY WORKING TOGETHER
TO RESHAPE THE WORLD

729
00:32:17.152 --> 00:32:20.114
TO OUR MUTUAL BENEFIT.

730
00:32:20.198 --> 00:32:22.461
[CROWD MURMURING]

731
00:32:24.507 --> 00:32:25.943
WELL DONE. RUSSELL.

732
00:32:27.336 --> 00:32:29.471
YOU'VE PASSED THE TRIAL.

733
00:32:29.555 --> 00:32:31.818
[APPLAUSE]

734
00:33:12.120 --> 00:33:14.299
AS OUR NEWEST MEMBER.

735
00:33:14.383 --> 00:33:16.040
YOU MAY NOW STEP FORWARD

736
00:33:16.124 --> 00:33:19.521
AND WIELD THE SOURCE
OF THIS GROUP'S POWER.

737
00:33:19.605 --> 00:33:21.523
WELL PLAYED. RUSSELL.

738
00:33:21.607 --> 00:33:24.048
YOU'RE SAVVIER
THAN I EXPECTED.

739
00:33:24.132 --> 00:33:27.312
PLEASE JOIN ME IN
WELCOMING RUSSELL TAN

740
00:33:27.396 --> 00:33:29.227
TO THE INNER SANCTUM.

741
00:33:29.311 --> 00:33:31.574
[APPLAUSE]

742
00:33:38.276 --> 00:33:39.498
[PHONE BUZZES]

743
00:33:39.582 --> 00:33:40.931
APOLOGIES.

744
00:33:44.413 --> 00:33:46.331
ALL RIGHT. RUSSELL.

745
00:33:46.415 --> 00:33:48.156
YOUR INITIATION
IS COMPLETE.

746
00:33:50.897 --> 00:33:51.684
NO.

747
00:33:51.768 --> 00:33:52.990
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

748
00:33:53.074 --> 00:33:56.297
YOU ALL PLAY
WITH THIS MALLET.

749
00:33:56.381 --> 00:33:58.256
FETISHIZE IT.

750
00:33:58.340 --> 00:33:59.735
LIKE CHILDREN.

751
00:33:59.819 --> 00:34:02.912
I ALONE UNDERSTAND
ITS TRUE POWER.

752
00:34:02.996 --> 00:34:05.872
AND ONLY I HAVE THE
TOOLS AND THE KNOWLEDGE

753
00:34:05.956 --> 00:34:08.179
TO UNLEASH THAT POWER.

754
00:34:08.263 --> 00:34:09.876
AND WHEN I DO.

755
00:34:09.960 --> 00:34:11.788
I WILL BE UNTOUCHABLE.

756
00:34:12.789 --> 00:34:16.013
THIS BELONGS WITH ME.

757
00:34:16.097 --> 00:34:18.711
[PHONES BUZZING]

758
00:34:18.795 --> 00:34:21.624
CHECK YOUR MESSAGES.

759
00:34:23.060 --> 00:34:28.373
CONTINGENCY.
YOUR HOMES. FAMILIES.

760
00:34:28.457 --> 00:34:30.070
ALL AT MY MERCY.

761
00:34:30.154 --> 00:34:32.203
I'VE BEEN PLANNING FOR MONTHS.

762
00:34:32.287 --> 00:34:35.075
LOOKING FOR WEAKNESSES
AND OPENINGS

763
00:34:35.159 --> 00:34:36.555
IN YOUR SECURITY.

764
00:34:36.639 --> 00:34:39.511
MY MEN ARE AT YOUR HOMES NOW...

765
00:34:41.165 --> 00:34:43.301
READY TO STRIKE.

766
00:34:43.385 --> 00:34:45.738
IF YOU LEAVE
THIS ROOM.

767
00:34:45.822 --> 00:34:48.085
HOW DO YOU THINK THINGS
ARE GONNA END UP FOR YOU?

768
00:34:49.478 --> 00:34:51.918
I HAVE THE ONLY COPY
OF FITZ RONSON'S

769
00:34:52.002 --> 00:34:54.657
EXPOSE ON
THE INNER SANCTUM.

770
00:34:56.137 --> 00:34:59.099
IF YOU ATTEMPT
TO RETALIATE.

771
00:34:59.183 --> 00:35:02.798
ALL YOUR DIRTY SECRETS
WILL BECOME PUBLIC.

772
00:35:02.882 --> 00:35:08.326
YOU HAVE NO CHOICE.
YOU WILL LET ME LEAVE

773
00:35:08.410 --> 00:35:10.937
WITH THE MALLET.

774
00:35:11.021 --> 00:35:12.109
NO!

775
00:35:16.331 --> 00:35:17.767
RUSSELL: NICKY SHEN.

776
00:35:19.986 --> 00:35:22.601
YOU CAME TO GET
THE MALLET BEFORE I COULD.

777
00:35:22.685 --> 00:35:23.906
GUESS YOU BEAT ME
TO IT.

778
00:35:23.990 --> 00:35:25.299
HENRY: CONGRATULATIONS.

779
00:35:25.383 --> 00:35:27.864
MAN: WHO THE HELL IS HE?
[CROWD CHATTERING]

780
00:35:30.649 --> 00:35:32.085
WHAT'S IN
THE BAG. NICKY?

781
00:35:40.181 --> 00:35:41.185
I HAVE TO SAY

782
00:35:41.269 --> 00:35:43.706
THIS IS EXCELLENT CRAFTSMANSHIP.

783
00:35:45.577 --> 00:35:47.417
NATHAN: WHAT ARE YOU DOING?
[MALLET HITS FLOOR]

784
00:35:48.754 --> 00:35:50.411
NATHAN: NO!

785
00:35:50.495 --> 00:35:52.715
DON'T WORRY. NATHAN.
IT'S FAKE.

786
00:35:54.020 --> 00:35:55.286
NO! [GRUNTS]

787
00:35:55.370 --> 00:35:56.722
HENRY: STOP.

788
00:35:56.806 --> 00:35:58.202
UHH!

789
00:35:58.286 --> 00:35:59.638
NATHAN: I DON'T KNOW
WHO YOU TWO ARE.

790
00:35:59.722 --> 00:36:04.208
BUT SECURITY WILL
SEE YOU OUT. NOW.

791
00:36:04.292 --> 00:36:07.907
HELP ME!
THEY'RE THIEVES!

792
00:36:07.991 --> 00:36:09.561
YOU GUYS
DON'T UNDERSTAND.

793
00:36:09.645 --> 00:36:11.215
MAN: ♪ PACK IT UP.
I'VE BEEN STEPPING ♪

794
00:36:11.299 --> 00:36:15.219
♪ IN A WORLD OF MY OWN...

795
00:36:15.303 --> 00:36:16.524
♪ GET ME OUT MY ZONE

796
00:36:16.608 --> 00:36:19.440
♪ ...GOT SO NERVOUS...

797
00:36:19.524 --> 00:36:22.922
♪ WATCH ME TURN
THE AWKWARD MOMENT... ♪

798
00:36:23.006 --> 00:36:25.272
[NICKY GRUNTING]

799
00:36:25.356 --> 00:36:28.751
TAN'S GOT THE MALLET AND THEY'RE
ONTO US. EVERYBODY OUT NOW.

800
00:36:30.274 --> 00:36:31.580
ALL DONE.

801
00:36:35.148 --> 00:36:39.068
MAN: ♪ PACK IT UP...

802
00:36:39.152 --> 00:36:43.331
♪ ...YOU SEE ME COMING.
BETTER PACK IT UP. WHAT ♪

803
00:36:44.506 --> 00:36:48.339
♪ PACK IT UP. YEAH.
PACK IT UP ♪

804
00:36:48.423 --> 00:36:49.728
TWO MORE GUARDS
INCOMING.

805
00:36:51.426 --> 00:36:53.746
- MIA: SHOULDN'T WE HELP THEM?
- RYAN: NICKY'S ORDERS. LET'S GO.

806
00:36:56.126 --> 00:36:58.302
[ALL GRUNTING]

807
00:37:03.089 --> 00:37:05.266
[ALL GRUNTING]

808
00:37:30.813 --> 00:37:31.857
UHH!

809
00:37:33.642 --> 00:37:35.734
NO. NICKY?
MIA TOOK OFF.

810
00:37:35.818 --> 00:37:37.820
MIA TOOK OFF.
SHE'S CHASING TAN.

811
00:37:43.913 --> 00:37:45.958
[ALL GRUNTING]

812
00:37:49.614 --> 00:37:52.008
MAN: AAH!
HENRY: GO. I GOT THIS.

813
00:37:55.620 --> 00:37:57.840
[ALL GRUNTING]

814
00:38:05.891 --> 00:38:06.936
STOP!

815
00:38:10.026 --> 00:38:14.033
RUSSELL: MIA!
MIA: YOU HUNTED ME DOWN.

816
00:38:14.117 --> 00:38:18.603
YOU KILLED MY FRIENDS.
YOU KILLED MY MOTHER.

817
00:38:18.687 --> 00:38:23.822
YOU WILL PAY
FOR WHAT YOU'VE DONE.

818
00:38:24.780 --> 00:38:27.435
[COCKS GUN]
CAREFUL.

819
00:38:28.436 --> 00:38:30.484
YOU NEED ME.

820
00:38:30.568 --> 00:38:32.965
YOU CAN'T SHOOT ME.

821
00:38:33.049 --> 00:38:35.399
RYAN: MIA!
MIA: RYAN. GET BACK!

822
00:38:38.097 --> 00:38:40.712
YOU'RE RIGHT.
I WON'T SHOOT YOU.

823
00:38:40.796 --> 00:38:44.060
[GUNSHOT] MIA: WHOA. NO! NO! OH. MY...

824
00:38:45.583 --> 00:38:50.243
RYAN! AHH! AAH!
I'M SORRY...

825
00:38:50.327 --> 00:38:52.547
[TIRES SCREECH]

826
00:38:53.852 --> 00:38:55.770
RYAN.

827
00:38:55.854 --> 00:38:56.899
MIA?

828
00:38:58.379 --> 00:39:01.559
RYAN. I'M SORRY.

829
00:39:01.643 --> 00:39:04.475
RYAN: UHH.
NICKY: RYAN? MIA?

830
00:39:04.559 --> 00:39:05.777
MIA?

831
00:39:08.519 --> 00:39:09.738
RYAN?

832
00:39:10.869 --> 00:39:15.007
[NICKY GASPING]
RYAN: NICKY?

833
00:39:15.091 --> 00:39:17.792
NICKY: CALL 911!
RYAN'S BEEN SHOT.

834
00:39:17.876 --> 00:39:20.096
[SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY]

835
00:39:21.924 --> 00:39:26.145
- STAY WITH ME. SOMEBODY HELP!
- [CRYING]

836
00:39:28.931 --> 00:39:29.975
RYAN?

837
00:39:30.933 --> 00:39:33.544
TAN WAS ABOUT TO GET AWAY.

838
00:39:36.417 --> 00:39:38.422
I THOUGHT I COULD STOP HIM.

839
00:39:38.506 --> 00:39:40.464
BUT IT ALL HAPPENED SO FAST.

840
00:39:43.336 --> 00:39:47.692
[SNIFFLES] RYAN.
SO MUCH BLOOD

841
00:39:47.776 --> 00:39:50.779
AND [SNIFFLES]
I TRIED.

842
00:39:52.476 --> 00:39:56.396
BUT IT'S... [SNIFFLES]
IT'S MY FAULT AND...

843
00:39:56.480 --> 00:39:58.743
NO. YOU DID THE RIGHT
THING COMING HERE.

844
00:40:00.528 --> 00:40:03.534
THEY'LL NEVER
FORGIVE YOU FOR THIS.

845
00:40:03.618 --> 00:40:04.839
[SNIFFLES]

846
00:40:04.923 --> 00:40:06.711
THEY WILL
NEVER UNDERSTAND

847
00:40:06.795 --> 00:40:10.758
THAT IT IS NOT
YOUR FAULT... IT'S NICKY'S.

848
00:40:10.842 --> 00:40:12.931
SHE CAN'T DO WHAT
NEEDS TO BE DONE.

849
00:40:14.237 --> 00:40:17.458
WE WILL KILL RUSSELL TAN...

850
00:40:19.198 --> 00:40:20.461
TOGETHER.

851
00:40:52.884 --> 00:40:54.495
MAN: <i>GREG. MOVE YOUR HEAD.</i>

